<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>NURUL HIDAYAH | Mega Cyber Interface</title>
    
    <!-- IBM Plex Sans & Orbitron Fonts -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://unpkg.com" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <style>
        :root {
            --electric-blue: #00d4ff;
            --ibm-blue: #0f62fe;
            --deep-navy: #001a66;
            --glass: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }

        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #001a66 0%, #0033cc 100%);
            color: #ffffff;
            margin: 0;
            font-family: 'IBM Plex Sans', sans-serif;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        /* Tipografi Cyber Glow */
        .cyber-title-main {
            font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
            font-size: 5.5rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            text-align: center;
            letter-spacing: 15px;
            color: #fff;
            text-shadow: 0 0 20px var(--electric-blue), 0 0 40px var(--ibm-blue);
            margin: 40px 0 20px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        /* BINGKAI PALING BESAR (MEGA FRAME) */
        .mega-hero-frame {
            width: 100%;
            height: 600px;
            border: 8px solid #fff;
            border-radius: 40px; /* Ujung dibulatkan halus */
            background: #000;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 0 50px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.4);
            margin-bottom: 80px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .mega-hero-frame img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            opacity: 0.8;
        }

        .scan-line-mega {
            position: absolute; width: 100%; height: 4px;
            background: var(--electric-blue);
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px var(--electric-blue);
            animation: scanVertical 6s infinite linear;
        }

        @keyframes scanVertical { 0% { top: 0; } 100% { top: 100%; } }

        /* Bingkai Umum dengan Ujung Bulat */
        .rounded-frame {
            border-radius: 20px;
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275);
            border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
        }

        .rounded-frame:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05) translateY(-10px);
            border-color: var(--electric-blue);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
        }

        .glass-card-3d {
            background: var(--glass);
            backdrop-filter: blur(15px);
            border-radius: 30px;
            padding: 40px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
        }

        /* Section Tags */
        .section-header {
            font-family: 'Orbitron';
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: var(--electric-blue);
            border-left: 8px solid #fff;
            padding-left: 20px;
            margin: 60px 0 30px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div id="particles-js" style="position: fixed; width: 100%; height: 100%; z-index: -1;"></div>

    <div class="main-wrapper" style="max-width: 1400px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
        
        <!-- HEADER: NURUL HIDAYAH -->
        <header data-aos="zoom-in">
            <h1 class="cyber-title-main">NURUL HIDAYAH</h1>
            <p style="text-align: center; font-family: 'Orbitron'; letter-spacing: 8px; color: #fff; opacity: 0.7;">
                INTEGRATED DIGITAL EDUCATIONAL ARCHIVE
            </p>
        </header>

        <!-- SATU BINGKAI PALING BESAR (Tepat di bawah Nurul Hidayah) -->
        <section class="mega-hero-frame" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="1500">
            <div class="scan-line-mega"></div>
            <!-- Masukkan foto dokumentasi utama/terbaik di sini -->
            <img src="/images/hero-dokumentasi.jpg" alt="Main Documentation">
            <div style="position: absolute; bottom: 30px; left: 40px; font-family: 'Orbitron'; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.7); padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 10px; border-left: 5px solid var(--electric-blue);">
                PRIMARY_ARCHIVE // DATA_SET: 00-A1
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- 15 BINGKAI SANGAT BESAR -->
        <h2 class="section-header">// CORE_UNITS: 15_LARGE_BENTLEY</h2>
        <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 30px; margin-bottom: 100px;">
            <% for(let i=1; i<=15; i++) { %>
                <div class="rounded-frame" style="height: 400px; background: var(--deep-navy);" data-aos="fade-up">
                    <div style="height: 100%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-family: 'Orbitron'; color: var(--electric-blue);">
                        LARGE_FRAME_<%= i %>
                    </div>
                </div>
            <% } %>
        </div>

        <!-- 25 BINGKAI SEDANG -->
        <h2 class="section-header">// ARCHIVE_DATA: 25_MEDIUM_POINTS</h2>
        <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr); gap: 20px; margin-bottom: 100px;">
            <% for(let j=1; j<=25; j++) { %>
                <div class="rounded-frame" style="height: 180px; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.2); border-style: dashed;" data-aos="zoom-in">
                    <div style="height: 100%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 0.7rem; opacity: 0.5;">
                        MED_FILE_<%= j %>
                    </div>
                </div>
            <% } %>
        </div>

        <!-- 8 BINGKAI STAFF BULAT (PENGELOLA) -->
        <h2 style="text-align: center; font-family: 'Orbitron'; font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 60px;">BOARD OF MANAGEMENT</h2>
        <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 40px; margin-bottom: 100px;">
            <% 
            const management = [
                {n: 'IMAT JUNAEDAH, S.Pd.I', r: 'Kepala Sekolah'},
                {n: 'ATANG ABDURAHMAN', r: 'Manager'},
                {n: 'MASPUPAH, S.Pd', r: 'Sekertaris'},
                {n: 'APIPULLOH ASHIDIQ, S.T.I', r: 'Operator'},
                {n: 'SRI INDAH', r: 'Guru'},
                {n: 'NABILA FAUZIAH', r: 'Guru'},
                {n: 'SALWA NOVIYANTI', r: 'Guru'},
                {n: 'JAJANG NURJAMAN', r: 'Bendahara'}
            ];
            %>
            <% management.forEach((s) => { %>
                <div style="text-align: center;" data-aos="fade-up">
                    <div style="width: 160px; height: 160px; border-radius: 50%; border: 4px solid #fff; margin: 0 auto 20px; background: #000; box-shadow: 0 0 25px var(--electric-blue); overflow: hidden; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">
                        <span style="font-family: 'Orbitron'; font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--electric-blue);">PHOTO</span>
                    </div>
                    <div style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 1.1rem;"><%= s.n %></div>
                    <div style="color: var(--electric-blue); font-family: 'Orbitron'; font-size: 0.7rem; letter-spacing: 2px;"><%= s.r %></div>
                </div>
            <% }); %>
        </div>

        <!-- VISI MISI KB & MI -->
        <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 40px; margin-bottom: 100px;">
            <div class="glass-card-3d" data-aos="fade-right">
                <h3 style="font-family: 'Orbitron'; color: var(--electric-blue); border-bottom: 2px solid #fff; padding-bottom: 15px;">KB NURUL HIDAYAH</h3>
                <p style="font-size: 1.2rem; line-height: 1.8; font-weight: 300;">
                    "Membentuk generasi Rabbani yang unggul, berakhlak mulia, dan adaptif terhadap perkembangan teknologi sejak usia dini."
                </p>
                <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; opacity: 0.7;">Pendidikan holistik yang mengintegrasikan nilai-nilai Tauhid dengan literasi digital dasar.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="glass-card-3d" data-aos="fade-left">
                <h3 style="font-family: 'Orbitron'; color: #fff; border-bottom: 2px solid var(--electric-blue); padding-bottom: 15px;">MI NURUL HIDAYAH</h3>
                <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.6;">
                    Tarbiyah, Ta'lim, dan Ta'dib: Penguasaan Ulumuddin mendalam serta karakter Islami Rahmatan lil 'Alamiin.
                </p>
                <ul style="color: var(--electric-blue); font-size: 0.9rem;">
                    <li>Madrasah Diniyah Takmiliyah</li>
                    <li>Fokus Pembentukan Karakter Peserta Didik</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- SEJARAH PENDIRI (PALING BAWAH) -->
        <section class="glass-card-3d" style="background: #fff; color: #001a66;" data-aos="fade-up">
            <h2 style="text-align: center; font-family: 'Orbitron'; font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 50px;">SEJARAH PENDIRIAN</h2>
            <div style="display: flex; gap: 60px; align-items: center;">
                <div style="width: 350px; flex-shrink: 0; text-align: center;">
                    <div style="border: 8px solid #001a66; border-radius: 30px; padding: 10px; background: #000; overflow: hidden;">
                        <div style="height: 400px; background: #001a66; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: #fff; font-family: 'Orbitron';">FOUNDER_IMG</div>
                    </div>
                    <p style="margin-top: 20px; font-weight: 900; font-family: 'Orbitron'; font-size: 1.2rem;">MUSTOFA, MUI</p>
                </div>
                <div style="flex: 1; line-height: 2; font-size: 1.2rem; text-align: justify; border-left: 5px solid var(--electric-blue); padding-left: 40px;">
                    <p>"Ponpes Nurul Hidayah didirikan dengan visi <strong>KH. MUSTOFA</strong> untuk menyinergikan kecerdasan intelektual dan spiritual. Sekolah ini tumbuh dari langkah-langkah kecil perjuangan tokoh ulama Indonesia demi masa depan generasi muda."</p>
                    <p>"Kami percaya setiap anak adalah amanah, dan sejarah kami adalah perjalanan menjaga amanah tersebut untuk generasi yang lebih baik."</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

    </div>

    <!-- Mandatory Scripts -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net"></script>
    <script src="https://unpkg.com"></script>
    <script>
        AOS.init({ duration: 1000, once: true });
        particlesJS('particles-js', {
            "particles": {
                "number": { "value": 80 },
                "color": { "value": "#ffffff" },
                "line_linked": { "color": "#ffffff", "opacity": 0.2 }
            }
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
